TRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\", \n    \"frontend->frontend:RecommendationService/ListRecommendations\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"frontend->frontend:Frontend/Recv\",\n    \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice:CartService/EmptyCart\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice:CartService/GetCart\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"RecommendationService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"RecommendationService/ListRecommendations调用延迟从正常124ms激增至56.6秒，延迟倍数高达456倍，是系统中最严重的延迟问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend服务返回HTTP 500错误，且RecommendationService调用出现大量'context canceled'错误，表明上游服务超时导致前端服务失败\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService的EmptyCart操作延迟从18ms增加到83ms，延迟倍数4.6倍，显示下游依赖可能存在性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService的GetCart操作延迟从2.5ms增加到8.1ms，延迟倍数3.2倍，表明购物车服务存在性能瓶颈\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **主要根因**: RecommendationService的严重性能问题，其ListRecommendations操作延迟激增456倍，导致整个调用链超时。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**: \n   - RecommendationService性能问题 → Frontend调用超时 → Frontend返回HTTP 500错误\n   - 大量\"context canceled\"错误表明上游服务因超时主动取消了请求\n\n3. **影响范围**: 所有三个Frontend实例都受到影响，表明这是系统级问题而非单点故障。\n\n4. **次要问题**: CheckoutService和CartService也存在轻微性能退化，但相比RecommendationService的问题影响较小。\n\n建议下一步深入分析RecommendationService的内部组件依赖关系，特别是其与ProductCatalogService的交互是否存在问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常高的 client_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 指标，表明服务在处理请求时出现大量错误。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_r